title: One died, two injured as snow boulder falls in Chitral | Pakistan - Geo.tv
text:
One died, two injured as snow boulder falls in Chitral | 0 0 
CHITRAL: One died while two others were injured when a boulder of snow fell on him on Sunday morning in Chitral, according to the police. 
Snowfall has started again in upper parts of the district while rain has started to pour again in Chitral city. 
Moreover, snowfall in Lower Top has caused electricity wires to break. Subsequently, power supply was suspended to parts of the district.
